Class AuthorizationCodeFlow.Builder

  • java.lang.Object

    AuthorizationCodeFlow

    public static class AuthorizationCodeFlow.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Authorization code flow builder.

    Implementation is not thread-safe.
